%% Revised Sequence: Balance Inquiry (sensitive) with EIDP/CIDP
%% Created by GitHub Copilot on 2026-03-01 for ADR-0104 Round 2 Review
%% Addresses EIDP/CIDP omission — shows full token chain

sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant CES as CX Agent Studio
  participant BFA as BFA Gateway (Cloud Run)
  participant CIDP as CIDP (Cloud Identity Provider)
  participant CIAM as ForgeRock CIAM (Customer Identity)
  participant PDP as AuthZ PDP
  participant AP as Apigee Internal
  participant Core as Core Banking SoR

  User->>CES: "What's my balance?"

  CES->>BFA: Tool call (Service Directory PNA)<br/>IAM ID token (service identity)<br/>headers: request_id, session_id, agent_id,<br/>tool_id, customer_id_hash, auth_level

  Note over BFA: Validate CES service identity (IAM ID token)<br/>Validate schema + mandatory correlation headers<br/>Classify intent as SENSITIVE (balance = PII data)

  BFA->>CIAM: RFC 8693 Token Exchange<br/>subject_token: customer session context<br/>scope: account:balance:read<br/>audience: acme-banking-agentic<br/>acr: requested assurance level

  CIAM-->>BFA: Agentic customer token<br/>(short-lived, audience-restricted,<br/>includes customer_id_hash + acr)

  BFA->>CIDP: Service token request<br/>(OAuth2 client_credentials over mTLS)<br/>audience: apigee-internal<br/>scope: banking.accounts.balance.read

  CIDP-->>BFA: CIDP service token<br/>(short-lived, audience: apigee-internal)

  BFA->>PDP: AuthZ decision request<br/>subject: customer (from agentic token)<br/>action: account.balance.read<br/>resource: accounts/*<br/>context: agent_id, auth_level/acr<br/>propagate: request_id, session_id, policy_decision_id

  PDP-->>BFA: Permit + obligations<br/>(redaction rules, data minimization)<br/>policy_decision_id: pdp-xxx

  Note over BFA: Route to Banking Adapter (internal)

  BFA->>AP: Call balance API (mTLS)<br/>Authorization: Bearer {agentic_token}<br/>X-Service-Token: {cidp_service_token}<br/>propagate: all correlation headers<br/>+ policy_decision_id

  AP->>Core: Private call to core banking SoR<br/>propagate: correlation headers

  Core-->>AP: Balance payload<br/>(account_id, balance, available_balance,<br/>currency, last_updated)

  AP-->>BFA: Normalized response<br/>+ upstream trace IDs

  Note over BFA: Apply PDP redaction obligations<br/>Mask account_id (show last 4 only)<br/>Strip internal metadata<br/>PII minimization before returning to CES

  BFA-->>CES: Sanitized response<br/>+ correlation IDs<br/>(only: masked_account, balance, currency)

  CES-->>User: Voice response:<br/>"Your checking account ending in 4532<br/>has a balance of €12,345.67"
